slinks back to his wife,

304
00:12:42,636 --> 00:12:45,097
and the whore ends up drunk
and alone.

305
00:12:45,181 --> 00:12:47,183
Actually,
now that I got four kids,

306
00:12:47,266 --> 00:12:48,809
