I caught you.

428
00:17:04,314 --> 00:17:05,274
I need fresh eyes
on an outfit.

429
00:17:05,357 --> 00:17:07,443
Uh, Simone
prefers the linen,

430
00:17:07,526 --> 00:17:09,445
but I think the navy's
more slimming.

431
00:17:09,528 --> 00:17:10,654
Thoughts?

432
00:17:10,738 --> 00:17:12,614
Y-You're not fat.

433
00:17:12,698 --> 00:17:14,783
