gave me.

436
00:17:19,413 --> 00:17:20,456
Ooh.

437
00:17:20,539 --> 00:17:21,832
Hark at you.

438
00:17:21,915 --> 00:17:23,584
Diamond Jim Brady Bunch.

439
00:17:23,667 --> 00:17:25,335
Anyway,

440
00:17:25,419 --> 00:17:26,462
